verbose_text: The measured mean levels of Ca were higher than those reported by Anshumali and Ramanathan [XREF_BIBR] and lower than those reported by Shomar et al. [XREF_BIBR] and the levels in Wielkie and Boszkowo Lakes, W. Poland [XREF_BIBR], while K, Na, and Mg levels were lower than the reported by Mastoi et al. [XREF_BIBR], Shomar et al. [XREF_BIBR] and Szymanowska et al. [XREF_BIBR].
